species-group. Besides the above mentioned species-groups, many other species which are not currently attributed to any species-group will be included. It also contains many species currently treated in the subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="E2C94D1CFFDAE67DCD2FF92B309FF8F9" authority="Bílý, 2019" authorityName="Bílý" authorityYear="2019" box="[615,716,1789,1814]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="266" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" sensu="stricto" status="s. str." subGenus="Anthaxia">
<emphasis id="17BDEA8DFFDAE67DCD2FF92B309FF8F9" box="[615,716,1789,1814]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="266">Anthaxia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="0C8E57F6FFDAE67DCD9CF929315CF8F9" box="[724,783,1791,1814]" pageId="5" pageNumber="266" sensu="stricto">s. str.</taxonomicNameLabel>
(
<bibRefCitation id="41584B6EFFDAE67DCC57F92B31CAF8F9" author="Bily, S." box="[799,921,1789,1814]" pageId="5" pageNumber="266" pagination="3 - 190" refId="ref11531" refString="Bily, S. (1997) World catalogue of the genus Anthaxia Eschscholtz, 1829 (Coleopreta, Buprestidae). Folia Heyrovskyana, Supplementum, 2, 3 - 190." type="journal article" year="1997">Bílý, 1997</bibRefCitation>
, 1999; 
<bibRefCitation id="41584B6EFFDAE67DCCA5F92B36C2F8F9" author="Bellamy, C. L." box="[1005,1169,1789,1814]" pageId="5" pageNumber="266" pagination="1261 - 1932" refId="ref11399" refString="Bellamy, C. L. (2008) A world catalogue and bibliography of the jewel beetles (Coleoptera: Buprestoidea). Volume 3. Buprestinae: Pterobothrini through Agrilinae: Rhaeboscelina. Pensoft series faunistica No. 78, Sofia-Moscow, pp. (1 - 2) + 1261 - 1932." type="book chapter" year="2008">Bellamy, 2008</bibRefCitation>
). On the contrary some species attributed currently to 
<taxonomicName id="E2C94D1CFFDAE67DCD48F8F730C9F8D5" authorityName="Reitter" authorityYear="1911" box="[512,666,1825,1850]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="275" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Haplanthaxia">
<emphasis id="17BDEA8DFFDAE67DCD48F8F730C9F8D5" box="[512,666,1825,1850]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="266">Haplanthaxia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
